title: Creativity benefits from order and chaos
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

Order brings consistency and stability.

Chaos brings randomness and variation.

By applying order into chaos, through structure, we can create value.

Evolution is a great example. It merges the chaos of mutation with the need for survival/stability to produce complex organisms.